00:04:16.940 --> 00:04:21.320
So you've got these gradients,
you've got sort of a

00:04:21.320 --> 00:04:24.340
semi-ActionBar at the top.

00:04:24.340 --> 00:04:25.260
ROMAN NURIK: The
faux ActionBar.

00:04:25.260 --> 00:04:27.330
ADAM KOCH: The faux ActionBar,
