00:04:27.330 --> 00:04:30.000
And you've got-- the drop-downs
spinners have the

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:34.020
little triangle to indicate the
spinner, but it's kind of

00:04:34.020 --> 00:04:35.600
half and half.

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:38.890
