00:04:40.790 --> 00:04:42.790
have the faux action bar.

00:04:42.790 --> 00:04:46.120
So simply switching the target
SDK out might actually remove

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:47.365
that kind of thing.

00:04:47.365 --> 00:04:48.810
Nick?

00:04:48.810 --> 00:04:51.005
