search history from the

00:08:05.240 --> 00:08:07.060
desktop to your devices
as well, that

00:08:07.060 --> 00:08:08.350
can be a killer feature.

00:08:08.350 --> 00:08:10.700
That can save you a bunch of
time, like Google Maps does,

00:08:10.700 --> 00:08:11.820
for example.

00:08:11.820 --> 00:08:12.650
ROMAN NURIK: Yeah, totally.

00:08:12.650 --> 00:08:13.250
Totally.

00:08:13.250 --> 00:08:15.070
Sync is-- that's like--

00:08:15.070 --> 00:08:16.640
in Russian, we would say
[SPEAKING RUSSIAN].

00:08:16.640 --> 00:08:18.870
That's like a whole
separate story.

00:08:18.870 --> 00:08:20.950
But sync, absolutely.

00:08:20.950 --> 00:08:24.820
That would make this whole
experience just like seamless.

00:08:24.820 --> 00:08:28.270
So yes, I have recent
searches.

00:08:28.270 --> 00:08:31.280
We simplified the entry
form and used icons.

00:08:31.280 --> 00:08:35.171
