same screen across

00:08:43.419 --> 00:08:45.530
different form factors.

00:08:45.530 --> 00:08:47.830
I feel like in this case they
could have just combined

00:08:47.830 --> 00:08:51.275
certain elements from both and
had less work to do when

00:08:51.275 --> 00:08:53.770
porting to different sizes.

00:08:53.770 --> 00:08:55.920
But anyway, so that's
kind of this screen.

00:08:55.920 --> 00:08:58.740
You'll notice that we did some
touch-ups on the map balloons

00:08:58.740 --> 00:09:01.370
